Mix Duncan Hines(R) Triple Chocolate Cake Mix as directed on box. Reserve the chocolate fudge pouch to be used in the filling. Do not mix into the cake. Spoon the batter into lined muffin pan. Bake for 18 mins. Allow to cool. While the cupcakes are baking, beat together the marshmallow fluff, the softened butter and the chocolate fudge pouch (mixed according to box with 1/3 cup water). Cool until firm enough to frost with or pipe into cupcakes. With pastry tip, pipe filling into center of cupcakes or cut a cone shape out of center of cupcake and fill with tablespoon of filling. Frost with favorite Duncan Hines(R) Frosting.